Package: CompareFragmentSize
Title: Compare fragment size between REF- and ALT- containing reads
Version: 0.0.16
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Stephenie",
           family = "Prokopec",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "stephenie.prokopec@uhn.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7936-8577"))
Description: Extracts reads overlapping a target variant and compares fragment size between REF- and ALT- containing reads to classify variant as somatic or non-somatic; useful for differentiating low-frequency somatic variants from CHIP or sequence artefacts in plasma cfDNA.
